			        <td valign="top" class="tableCell"><span id="speakerTitleCompanyLabel">Creative Director, Backbone Entertainment</span></td>
		        </tr>
		        <tr>
			        <td valign="top" class="tableCell"><span id="speakerBioLabel">As a journalist, Trent Ward worked on the launches of PC Gamer, Next Generation, Gamespot and IGN PC. After ten years, Trent left journalism to serve as Co-Director of the Australian Game Developers Conference. Here he got involved with Australian game design students, worked with many of the great design houses Down Under and enjoyed an opportunity to address controversial game issues on national radio while drinking at a pub. For the last two years, Trent has been in Canada working on the development side first as Senior Producer and more recently as Creative Director for Backbone Entertainment's Vancouver studio.</span></td>
